						               													<description>You and your people emerge from a glistening fog into a sprawling world much like your own, yet...fabricated? At your backs lie the unending silver dunes you came from. To the east and west stand massive walls that could only be the work of an intelligence much greater than your own. And crackling over the horizon is a massive storm that pulses with an otherworldly glow. Your resources are low, time is short...and you are not alone.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;In Suns of Chronos, control one of four races and explore a world full of strange lifeforms and mysterious artifacts. Manage your people and your time wisely, between exploiting the wonders of Chronos - such as the time-defying &amp;quot;sunstones&amp;quot; - and thwarting those who get in your way. Be wary, however. Besides your rivals, Chronos contains entities of its own that will challenge not only your people, but the very fabric of time upon which you depend.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;On the machine world of Chronos, those who carry out the will of their people best will go on to see a new universe. The rest will be lost to the sands of time.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
